embAc.what: Active element is embedded in a link or button

focInd.what: Focused element displaying no or nostandard focus indicator

focOp.what: Operable elements that cannot be Tab-focused and vice versa

aria-allowed-role.what: ARIA role is not appropriate for the element

styleDiff.what: Heading, link, and button style inconsistencies

r18.what: ARIA state or property is not allowed for the element on which it is specified

r19.what: ARIA state or property has an invalid value

r57.what: Perceivable text content is not included in any landmark

region.what: Some page content is not contained by landmarks

r66.what: Text contrast less than AAA requires

color-contrast-enhanced.what: Element has insufficient color contrast (Level AAA)

r69.what: Text outside widget has subminimum contrast

r73.what: Paragraph of text has insufficient line height

r78.what: No content between two headings of the same level

hidden-content.what: Some content is hidden and therefore may not be testable for accessibility

css-orientation-lock.what: CSS media query locks display orientation

landmark-unique.what: Landmark has a role and an accessible name that are identical to another

e:AA.2_4_1.H64.1.what: iframe element has no non-empty title attribute

e:AA.4_1_2.H91.InputText.Name.what: Text input has no accessible name

w:AA.1_3_1.H42.what: Heading coding is not used but the element may be intended as a heading

w:AA.1_3_1.H48.what: Navigation links are not coded as a list

w:AA.1_3_1.H85.2.what: Selection list may contain groups of related options that are not grouped with optgroup

155.what: Headings are not structured in a hierarchical manner

w:AA.1_4_10.C32,C31,C33,C38,SCR34,G206.what: Fixed-position element may force bidirectional scrolling

w:AA.1_4_3.G145.Abs.what: Contrast between the absolutely positioned large text and its background may be less than 3:1

w:AA.1_4_3.G18.Abs.what: Contrast between the absolutely positioned text and its background may be inadequate

w:AA.1_4_3.G18.BgImage.what: Contrast between the text and its background image may be less than 4.5:1

w:AA.1_4_3_F24.F24.BGColour.what: Inline background color may lack a complementary foreground color

w:AA.4_1_2.H91.A.Placeholder.what: Link has text but no href, id, or name attribute

w:AA.4_1_2.H91.Select.Value.what: Select element value has no accessible name

a:link_redundant.what: Adjacent links go to the same URL

a:noscript.what: noscript element may fail to contain an accessible equivalent or alternative

a:underline.what: CSS underline on text that is not a link

129.what: CSS underline on text that is not a link

98.what: Links have the same text but different destinations

144.what: Line height is insufficent to properly display the computed font size

152.what: Actionable element is smaller than the minimum required size

218.what: Link opens in a new window without user control
